new.name: MCP-Inspector-CVE-2025-49596
new.description: MCP-Inspector-vulncheck is a Python script that checks if an MCP Inspector server is vulnerable to CVE-2025-49596. It tests whether the /sse endpoint responds to unauthenticated requests, indicating a potential security flaw. The script is simple to use and provides clear output on whether the target server is likely vulnerable or patched.
